8\u5948\u304c2\u4f5c\u9023\u7d9a\u30bb\u30f3\u30bf\u30fc \u9577\u6ff1\u306d\u308b\u304c\u521d\u9078\u629c|accessdate=2016-08-10|publisher=oricon ME inc.|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n* 2nd row: [[Mizuho Habu]], [[Neru Nagahama]], [[Y\u016bka Sugai]], [[Akane Moriya]], Miyu Suzumoto, [[Yui Kobayashi]]<ref name=\"oricon20160627\"/>\n* 3rd row: Nana Oda, Fuyuka Sait\u014d, Aoi Harada, Rina Uemura, Nanako Nagasawa, Minami Koike, Rika Ozeki, Nanami Yonetani, Shiori Sat\u014d, Nijika Ishimori<ref name=\"oricon20160627\"/>\n\n=== \"Kataru Nara Mirai o...\" ===\n* Nijika Ishimori, Yui Imaizumi, Rina Uemura, Rika Ozeki, Nana Oda, Minami Koike, Yui Kobayashi, Fuyuka Sait\u014d, Shiori Sat\u014d, Manaka Shida, Y\u016bka Sugai, Miyu Suzumoto, Nanako Nagasawa, Mizuho Habu, Aoi Harada, [[Yurina Hirate]], Akane Moriya, Nanami Yonetani, Rika Watanabe, Risa Watanabe, Neru Nagahama<ref name=\"official_2nd\">{{cite web|url=http://www.keyakizaka46.com/mob/pageShw.php?cd=2ndsingle_detail|script-title=ja:2nd\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u8a73\u7d30|accessdate=2016-08-10|publisher=Keyakizaka46 Official Website|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n\n=== \"Shibuya Kara Parco ga Kieta Hi\" ===\n* [[Yurina Hirate]]<ref name=\"official_2nd\"/>\n\n=== \"Mata Atte Kudasai\" ===\n* Neru Nagahama<ref name=\"official_2nd\"/>\n\n=== \"Aozora ga Chigau\" ===\n* Manaka Shida, Y\u016bka Sugai, Akane Moriya, Rika Watanabe, Risa Watanabe<ref name=\"official_2nd\"/>\n\n=== \"Bob Dylan wa Kaesanai\" ===\n* Yui Imaizumi, Yui Kobayashi<ref name=\"official_2nd\"/>\n\n=== \"Hiragana Keyaki\" ===\n* Mao Iguchi, Sarina Ushio, Memi Kakizaki, Y\u016bka Kageyama, Shiho Kat\u014d, Ky\u014dko Sait\u014d, Kumi Sasaki, Mirei Sasaki, Mana Takase, Ayaka Takamoto, Neru Nagahama, Mei Higashimura<ref name=\"official_2nd\"/>\n\n== Chart and certifications ==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Weekly charts ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"1\"\n|-\n! Chart (2016)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n| Japan ([[Oricon]] Weekly [[Oricon Singles Chart|Singles Chart]])\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/670123/products/1187950/1/|script-title=ja: \u4e16\u754c\u306b\u306f\u611b\u3057\u304b\u306a\u3044(TYPE-A) \u6b05\u574246|work= Oricon Style|publisher= [[Oricon]]|accessdate= August 17, 2016|language= Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n| Japan (''[[Billboard Japan]]'' [[Japan Hot 100|Hot 100]])\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1<ref name=\"billboard\"/>\n|}\n\n=== Year-end charts ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Chart (2016)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n| Japan (Oricon Yearly Singles Chart)\n|align=\"center\"| 13<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/js/y/2016/p/2/|script-title=ja:\u30aa\u30ea\u30b3\u30f3\u5e74\u9593 CD\u30b7\u30f3\u30b0\u30eb\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 2016\u5e74\u5ea6|accessdate=2017-01-08|publisher=oricon ME|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n| Billboard Japan Hot100\n|align=\"center\"| 32\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Certifications ===\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Japan|type=single|artist=Keyakizaka46|title=Futari Saison|award=Platinum|certyear=2016|certmonth=8|relyear=2016|certref=<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.riaj.or.jp/f/data/cert/gd.html|script-title=ja:\u30b4\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u30c7\u30a3\u30b9\u30af\u8a8d\u5b9a 2016\u5e748\u6708|access-date=2017-01-08|publisher=RIAJ|language=Japanese}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|nosales=yes}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{cite book|last1=Keyakizaka46|date=10 August 2016a|title=Sekai ni wa Ai Shika Nai|edition=Type-A|publisher=Sony Music Entertainment|asin=B01GQ8PM4I|id=SRCL-9147/9148|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Keyakizaka46|date=10 August 2016b|title=Sekai ni wa Ai Shika Nai|edition=Type-B|publisher=Sony Music Entertainment|asin=B01GQ8PP72|id=SRCL-9149/9150|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Keyakizaka46|date=10 August 2016c|title=Sekai ni wa Ai Shika Nai|edition=Type-C|publisher=Sony Music Entertainment|asin=B01